name: The Deep Blue Ocean Base
description: After crashing into what is several traps of the sick-minded UAC officials' bases where they have been caught bringing in the demons themselves on purpose, you manage to escape these abominable traps and are led into what appears to be the ocean. You swim down deep and come across their secret ocean base. After being crushed down by what was a gigantic demon fecal matter, smacked sense into by a gigantic brown boat, and molested by a few psychopathic ladies you can only hope... Hope that you will find the solitude you seek...
